Packages 
Package Description
FestivalPlanner.Agenda
Contains classes relevant to data displayed in the scheduling parts of the GUI.
FestivalPlanner.GUI
Contains all classes relevant to graphical representation of our software.
FestivalPlanner.GUI.AgendaGUI
Contains classes related to elements drawn on screen, such as objects used by JavaFX.
FestivalPlanner.GUI.AgendaGUI.PopUpGUI
Contains PopUps used for Object creation in the AgendaGUI software.
FestivalPlanner.GUI.SimulatorGUI
Contains all GUI class related to the simulator-module.
FestivalPlanner.Logic
Contains simulator logic classes.
FestivalPlanner.NPC
Contains classes related to NPCs.
FestivalPlanner.TileMap
Contains classes responsible for handling the graphical representation/simulation of our software in the form of TileMaps.
FestivalPlanner.Util
Contains packages related to returning and/or setting values from files and/or the user's system settings.
FestivalPlanner.Util.JsonHandling
Contains classes for converting .JSON files into usable TileMaps for our software.
FestivalPlanner.Util.LanguageHandling
Contains classes related to resource bundles and general language handling.
FestivalPlanner.Util.MathHandling
Contains classed related to calculating and/or converting values.
FestivalPlanner.Util.PreferencesHandling
Contains all classes related to settings and preferences handling.
FestivalPlanner.Util.SoundHandling
Contains classes related to playing and getting sounds.
